    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 1. Validation results demonstrate CFD predictions of hemolysis index within ±15% of experimental measurements across all five operating points. RH < 1 criterion satisfied. The model is deemed credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. An informal screening sensitivity study confirmed robustness of worst-case identification to boundary condition perturbations, supporting confidence in the decision.",
